title: ATN midseason awards
itunes:title: ATN midseason awards
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – discuss the latest news from around the NFL, including the Titans firing head coach Ken Whisenhunt, and the 49ers benching quarterback Colin Kaepernick for Blaine Gabbert. Then the heroes present the "Around the NFL Midseason Awards" before finishing off with a preview of the Thursday night game between the Bengals and the Browns.
